    SELECT `u`.`Id`, `u`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u`.`CreationTime`, `u`.`CreatorUserId`, `u`.`DeleterUserId`, `u`.`DeletionTime`, `u`.`EmailAddress`, `u`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u`.`IsActive`, `u`.`IsDeleted`, `u`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u`.`LastModificationTime`, `u`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u`.`Name`, `u`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u`.`Password`, `u`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u`.`PhoneNumber`, `u`.`SecurityStamp`, `u`.`Surname`, `u`.`TenantId`, `u`.`UserName`
    FROM `Users` AS `u`
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))
) AS `t0` ON `t`.`UserId` = `t0`.`Id`
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT `u0`.`Id`, `u0`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u0`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u0`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u0`.`CreationTime`, `u0`.`CreatorUserId`, `u0`.`DeleterUserId`, `u0`.`DeletionTime`, `u0`.`EmailAddress`, `u0`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u0`.`IsActive`, `u0`.`IsDeleted`, `u0`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u0`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u0`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u0`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u0`.`LastModificationTime`, `u0`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u0`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u0`.`Name`, `u0`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u0`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u0`.`Password`, `u0`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u0`.`PhoneNumber`, `u0`.`SecurityStamp`, `u0`.`Surname`, `u0`.`TenantId`, `u0`.`UserName`
    FROM `Users` AS `u0`
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u0`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u0`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))
) AS `t1` ON `t`.`OwnerId` = `t1`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id` DESC

SELECT `t`.`Id`, `t`.`Introduce`, `t`.`IsApprove`, `t`.`OwnerId`, `t`.`UserId`, `t0`.`Id`, `t0`.`AccessFailedCount`, `t0`.`AuthenticationSource`, `t0`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `t0`.`CreationTime`, `t0`.`CreatorUserId`, `t0`.`DeleterUserId`, `t0`.`DeletionTime`, `t0`.`EmailAddress`, `t0`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `t0`.`IsActive`, `t0`.`IsDeleted`, `t0`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `t0`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `t0`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `t0`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `t0`.`LastModificationTime`, `t0`.`LastModifierUserId`, `t0`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `t0`.`Name`, `t0`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `t0`.`NormalizedUserName`, `t0`.`Password`, `t0`.`PasswordResetCode`, `t0`.`PhoneNumber`, `t0`.`SecurityStamp`, `t0`.`Surname`, `t0`.`TenantId`, `t0`.`UserName`, `t1`.`Id`, `t1`.`AccessFailedCount`, `t1`.`AuthenticationSource`, `t1`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `t1`.`CreationTime`, `t1`.`CreatorUserId`, `t1`.`DeleterUserId`, `t1`.`DeletionTime`, `t1`.`EmailAddress`, `t1`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `t1`.`IsActive`, `t1`.`IsDeleted`, `t1`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `t1`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `t1`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `t1`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `t1`.`LastModificationTime`, `t1`.`LastModifierUserId`, `t1`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `t1`.`Name`, `t1`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `t1`.`NormalizedUserName`, `t1`.`Password`, `t1`.`PasswordResetCode`, `t1`.`PhoneNumber`, `t1`.`SecurityStamp`, `t1`.`Surname`, `t1`.`TenantId`, `t1`.`UserName`
FROM (
    SELECT `f`.`Id`, `f`.`Introduce`, `f`.`IsApprove`, `f`.`OwnerId`, `f`.`UserId`
    FROM `Friends` AS `f`
    WHERE (`f`.`UserId` = @__userId_0) AND NOT (`f`.`IsApprove`)
    ORDER BY `f`.`Id` DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS `t`

FROM (
    SELECT `f`.`Id`, `f`.`Introduce`, `f`.`IsApprove`, `f`.`OwnerId`, `f`.`UserId`
    FROM `Friends` AS `f`
    WHERE (`f`.`UserId` = @__userId_0) AND NOT (`f`.`IsApprove`)
    ORDER BY `f`.`Id` DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT `u`.`Id`, `u`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u`.`CreationTime`, `u`.`CreatorUserId`, `u`.`DeleterUserId`, `u`.`DeletionTime`, `u`.`EmailAddress`, `u`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u`.`IsActive`, `u`.`IsDeleted`, `u`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u`.`LastModificationTime`, `u`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u`.`Name`, `u`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u`.`Password`, `u`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u`.`PhoneNumber`, `u`.`SecurityStamp`, `u`.`Surname`, `u`.`TenantId`, `u`.`UserName`
    FROM `Users` AS `u`
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))

        SELECT `u1`.`Id`, `u1`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u1`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u1`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u1`.`CreationTime`, `u1`.`CreatorUserId`, `u1`.`DeleterUserId`, `u1`.`DeletionTime`, `u1`.`EmailAddress`, `u1`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u1`.`IsActive`, `u1`.`IsDeleted`, `u1`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u1`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u1`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u1`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u1`.`LastModificationTime`, `u1`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u1`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u1`.`Name`, `u1`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u1`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u1`.`Password`, `u1`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u1`.`PhoneNumber`, `u1`.`SecurityStamp`, `u1`.`Surname`, `u1`.`TenantId`, `u1`.`UserName`
        FROM `Users` AS `u1`
        WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u1`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u1`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))
    ) AS `t2` ON `b1`.`MembersId` = `t2`.`Id`
) AS `t1` ON `b`.`Id` = `t1`.`BoardId`
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`Amount`, `c`.`BoardId`, `c`.`CreationTime`, `c`.`CreatorUserId`, `c`.`DeleterUserId`, `c`.`DeletionTime`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`IsDeleted`, `c`.`LastModificationTime`, `c`.`LastModifierUserId`, `c`.`OwnerId`, `c`.`Title`
    FROM `Cards` AS `c`
    WHERE @__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`c`.`IsDeleted`)
) AS `t3` ON `b`.`Id` = `t3`.`BoardId`
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`b`.`IsDeleted`)) AND ((`b`.`OwnerId` = @__AbpSession_UserId_0) OR EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM `BoardMembers` AS `b0`
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT `u`.`Id`, `u`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u`.`CreationTime`, `u`.`CreatorUserId`, `u`.`DeleterUserId`, `u`.`DeletionTime`, `u`.`EmailAddress`, `u`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u`.`IsActive`, `u`.`IsDeleted`, `u`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u`.`LastModificationTime`, `u`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u`.`Name`, `u`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u`.`Password`, `u`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u`.`PhoneNumber`, `u`.`SecurityStamp`, `u`.`Surname`, `u`.`TenantId`, `u`.`UserName`
        FROM `Users` AS `u`
        WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))
    ) AS `t` ON `b0`.`MembersId` = `t`.`Id`
    WHERE (`b`.`Id` = `b0`.`BoardId`) AND (`t`.`Id` = @__AbpSession_UserId_0)))
ORDER BY `b`.`Id`, `t0`.`Id`, `t1`.`BoardId`, `t1`.`MembersId`, `t1`.`Id`

    SELECT `u0`.`Id`, `u0`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u0`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u0`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u0`.`CreationTime`, `u0`.`CreatorUserId`, `u0`.`DeleterUserId`, `u0`.`DeletionTime`, `u0`.`EmailAddress`, `u0`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u0`.`IsActive`, `u0`.`IsDeleted`, `u0`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u0`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u0`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u0`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u0`.`LastModificationTime`, `u0`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u0`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u0`.`Name`, `u0`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u0`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u0`.`Password`, `u0`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u0`.`PhoneNumber`, `u0`.`SecurityStamp`, `u0`.`Surname`, `u0`.`TenantId`, `u0`.`UserName`
    FROM `Users` AS `u0`
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 OR NOT (`u0`.`IsDeleted`)) AND (@__ef_filter__p_1 OR (`u0`.`TenantId` = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_2))
) AS `t1` ON `t`.`OwnerId` = `t1`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id` DESC

    FROM `Friends` AS `f`
    WHERE (`f`.`OwnerId` = @__userId_0) AND NOT (`f`.`IsApprove`)
    ORDER BY `f`.`Id` DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS `t`

    SELECT `u`.`Id`, `u`.`AccessFailedCount`, `u`.`AuthenticationSource`, `u`.`ConcurrencyStamp`, `u`.`CreationTime`, `u`.`CreatorUserId`, `u`.`DeleterUserId`, `u`.`DeletionTime`, `u`.`EmailAddress`, `u`.`EmailConfirmationCode`, `u`.`IsActive`, `u`.`IsDeleted`, `u`.`IsEmailConfirmed`, `u`.`IsLockoutEnabled`, `u`.`IsPhoneNumberConfirmed`, `u`.`IsTwoFactorEnabled`, `u`.`LastModificationTime`, `u`.`LastModifierUserId`, `u`.`LockoutEndDateUtc`, `u`.`Name`, `u`.`NormalizedEmailAddress`, `u`.`NormalizedUserName`, `u`.`Password`, `u`.`PasswordResetCode`, `u`.`PhoneNumber`, `u`.`SecurityStamp`, `u`.`Surname`, `u`.`TenantId`, `u`.`UserName`
